<strong>Why You Need It</strong>

Many of these devices will help to save your home in a fire by alerting you of the danger while you are away. However, they can also be helpful for anyone who suffers from various allergies or is sensitive to high pollutants in the air and can truly create peace of mind when, say, you are in the office and your children are at home. You know your home is safe and that your family has a safe place to be, full of clean air.
