Nest also offers a <a href="https://nest.com/support/article/What-are-the-pricing-differences-for-Nest-Aware-subscription-plans" target="_blank">monthly upgrade package</a> that will allow 24/7 continuous video recording, as well as an up to 30-day history of those recordings. This can be especially helpful if youÂ <em>doÂ </em>experience a break-in or vandalism outside your home, because video recordings can catch the perpetrator and be valuable in working with the police to bring them to justice.
